      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear you. The pain you're feeling is immense, and it can feel like there's no way out. But sometimes, even when it seems like the cost of rebuilding is too high, finding a way through the suffering can lead to healing. It's not easy, and it might not feel like it right now, but you don't have to go through this alone. There are people who care about you and want to help you find a way to move forward, even if it's just one small step at a time. You don't have to face this alone.",
